{"tid":1527614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［9.2罷課］ 大家要記得罷課阿！","createTime":"2019-09-01T10:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T12:10:33.000Z","uid":315929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a72b593ab57faee4d14c56d4055e8c8f19d333a6","tid":1527614,"uid":315929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好關心而家鄉東涌嘅手足 我都唔例外<br />\n但係大家記得9.2嘅罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾日前 <strong>愛丁堡廣場反修例罷課集會</strong> 啲畜生出左不反對通知書 <br />\n作為今年新生 我好希望見到師兄師姐你地阿❤️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據警方不反對通知書，這場「反送中罷課」集會批准在上午8時至下午11時59分、於中環愛丁堡廣場西面行人路近郵政總局舉行。香港眾志早前表示，新界區學生可到中大百萬大道參與由10間大學學生會號召的罷課集會。"},{"pid":"51fb6073c53f779390f4b7ab02d7f89f8587c96e","tid":1527614,"uid":315929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"求下你地🥺"},{"pid":"cc834cc34a99fdfde88b8f731452c146280c631c","tid":1527614,"uid":315929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"一定要出席啊"},{"pid":"f3024fd4fc51062c962738f0912c7714035de152","tid":1527614,"uid":315929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"我要見到你地阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e959fa943f518e9f93ddbed9cbfdcd8ddf5887fb","tid":1527614,"uid":311055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3024fd4fc51062c962738f0912c7714035de152","tid":1527614,"uid":315929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"我要見到你地阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"著黑衫？"},{"pid":"935082026ad37c36169176c8b64045b99ccc56df","tid":1527614,"uid":315929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e959fa943f518e9f93ddbed9cbfdcd8ddf5887fb","tid":1527614,"uid":311055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3024fd4fc51062c962738f0912c7714035de152","tid":15276